        <abstract> 
<p>Gives an account of his publication plans for his and Ernst Krause’s <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>CD has never even dreamed of publishing his own autobiography.</p>
            <p>Is now working, with Francis, on plant movements.</p>
